{
  "text": "Based on previous studies, the incidence of phlebitis was found to be 50%. [CITATION_1] We hypothesized the incidence of phlebitis as 35% and with an alpha error of 5% and a power of 95%, sample size estimation showed 138 patients required for the study. We included 150 patients to increase statistical power.",
